lead_paragraph: Hillary Clinton will celebrate Labor Day with an edge over rival Donald Trump in any number of the most competitive states, even as she struggles with the challenge of sealing the deal with large groups of voters who consider her dishonest and untrustworthy.

headline.main: What's on Hillary Clinton's To-Do List Before Election Day?
